    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chicken stock</strong> to the pan and cook for 2-3 min or until the sauce starts to thicken</p><p>Once thickened, remove the pan from the heat and stir through your <strong>Dijon mustard</strong> (not a mustard fan? Go easy!) and <strong>crème fraîche </strong>– this is your <strong>creamy leek sauce</strong></p>",
