    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the <strong>drained potatoes</strong> to a low heat with a knob of <strong>butter</strong> and a splash of <strong>milk</strong>,<strong> </strong>then season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Mash until smooth – this is your<strong> buttery mash</strong></p>",
